---
---

<div class="upload-section">
  <div class="upload-left">
    <div>
      <h2 class="upload-left-title">¿Estuviste<br />esta semana?</h2>
      <p class="upload-left-sub">
        Sube tu foto del finde, consigue votos y gana el premio de la semana
        siguiente.
      </p>
    </div>
    <button class="upload-btn">
      <span>↑</span> Subir foto
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="upload-right">
    <div class="upload-rule">
      <div class="upload-rule-num">01</div>
      <div class="upload-rule-text">
        <strong>Sin registro</strong>
        <span>Solo tu foto y un nombre. Máximo 3 fotos por semana.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="upload-divider"></div>
    <div class="upload-rule">
      <div class="upload-rule-num">02</div>
      <div class="upload-rule-text">
        <strong>La comunidad vota</strong>
        <span
          >Cada persona puede votar una vez por foto. Votos visibles en tiempo
          real.</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="upload-divider"></div>
    <div class="upload-rule">
      <div class="upload-rule-num">03</div>
      <div class="upload-rule-text">
        <strong>Premio el finde siguiente</strong>
        <span>La foto ganadora se anuncia cada viernes. Premio en el local.</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .upload-section {
    padding: 80px 40px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .upload-left {
    background: var(--accent);
    padding: 60px 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .upload-left-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    color: var(--bg);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .upload-left-sub {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(8, 8, 16, 0.6);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 300px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .upload-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 28px;
    border: none;
    cursor: none;
    width: fit-content;
    transition:
      transform 0.15s,
      box-shadow 0.15s;
  }
  .upload-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }
  .upload-right {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 60px 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 28px;
  }
  .upload-rule {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .upload-rule-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 50px;
  }
  .upload-rule-text strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .upload-rule-text span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .upload-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .upload-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .upload-left,
    .upload-right {
      padding: 48px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
